text: Jadaun or Jadon is a clan of the rajput community. It is believed once they ruled the state of Mathura and later shifted to Bayana and Karauli. They claim descent from the Yaduvanshi Rajput lineage. == References == Category:Jat clans Category:Gurjar clans Category:Ahir clans category:Rajput clans
